我这个脚本，后续实机评估的时候需要usb识别相机，还要接收/hdas/feedback_gripper_left \ 
/hdas/feedback_gripper_right \ 
/motion_control/pose_ee_arm_left \ 
/motion_control/pose_ee_arm_right \ 的ros反馈的状态信息，还要输出ros2 topic pub /motion_target/target_pose_arm_left geometry_msgs/msg/PoseStamped \
"{
  header: {
    stamp: {sec: 0, nanosec: 0},
    frame_id: 'base_link'    
  },
  pose: {
    position: {
      x: 0.2,  
      y: 0.25,  
      z: -0.3   
    },
    orientation: {
      x: 0.0,  
      y: 0.0,  
      z: 0.0,   
      w: 1.0    
    }
  }
}"
ros2 topic pub /motion_target/target_pose_arm_right geometry_msgs/msg/PoseStamped \
"{
  header: {
    stamp: {sec: 0, nanosec: 0},
    frame_id: 'base_link'    
  },
  pose: {
    position: {
      x: 0.2,  
      y: 0.25,  
      z: -0.3   
    },
    orientation: {
      x: 0.0,  
      y: 0.0,  
      z: 0.0,   
      w: 1.0    
    }
  }
}"+ros2 topic pub /motion_target/target_position_gripper_left sensor_msgs/msg/JointState '{header: {stamp: {sec: 0, nanosec: 0}, frame_id: ""}, name: ["R1PRO_left_gripper_joint"], position: [0.0]}'的控制指令
